WEBVTT

00:00:03.819 --> 00:00:06.820
Jehovah's Witnesses were proclaiming that the solution

00:00:06.820 --> 00:00:09.820
to the world's problems rests with God's government.

00:00:09.820 --> 00:00:15.519
On the other hand, the Churches repeatedly voiced support

00:00:15.519 --> 00:00:18.519
for human governments.

00:00:18.519 --> 00:00:21.519
Jehovah's Witnesses felt a responsibility

00:00:21.519 --> 00:00:24.519
to make people aware of the position being taken

00:00:24.519 --> 00:00:27.519
by their religious leaders.

00:00:27.519 --> 00:00:32.520
In 1938, more than 10,000 people jammed into London's

00:00:32.520 --> 00:00:35.520
Royal Albert Hall to hear a pointed lecture

00:00:35.520 --> 00:00:38.520
by Joseph Rutherford, while millions more

00:00:38.520 --> 00:00:41.520
heard this stinging message by radio.

00:00:41.520 --> 00:00:45.520
Always outspoken, Rutherford invited his listeners

00:00:45.520 --> 00:00:49.520
to face the facts.

00:00:49.520 --> 00:00:53.520
The dictator of the totalitarian rule of Germany

00:00:53.520 --> 00:00:56.520
has entered into an alliance with the Pope.

00:00:56.520 --> 00:01:00.520
The indisputable facts are that the Roman Catholic hierarchy

00:01:00.520 --> 00:01:03.520
has stooped wholly to political methods

00:01:03.520 --> 00:01:08.519
to gain control of the world.

00:01:08.519 --> 00:01:10.519
Rutherford pointed to the Church's role

00:01:10.519 --> 00:01:13.519
in the rise of Adolf Hitler.

00:01:13.519 --> 00:01:16.519
It's alliances with fascist regimes

00:01:16.519 --> 00:01:19.519
and its push in many nations to make Catholicism

00:01:19.519 --> 00:01:21.519
the state religion.

00:01:21.519 --> 00:01:32.590
When World War II erupted in 1939,

00:01:32.590 --> 00:01:34.590
nearly every organized religion

00:01:34.590 --> 00:01:39.930
sent its members into the battle.

00:01:39.930 --> 00:01:41.930
French and American Catholics killed German

00:01:41.930 --> 00:01:44.930
and Italian Catholics.

00:01:44.930 --> 00:01:51.370
British and American Protestants killed German Protestants.

00:01:51.370 --> 00:01:54.370
Jehovah's Witnesses wanted to make it clear

00:01:54.370 --> 00:01:58.739
that they were no part of this controversy.

00:01:58.739 --> 00:02:02.739
The watchtower of November 1, 1939 reasoned,

00:02:02.739 --> 00:02:06.739
how could a person who is devoted to God's Kingdom

00:02:06.739 --> 00:02:09.740
favor one side or the other in a conflict

00:02:09.740 --> 00:02:12.740
between factions of the world?
